</div>
</div>

<div class="chat-message bot-message">
<div class="message-avatar">🦞</div>
<div class="message-content">
<div class="message-text">今天感觉怎么样？可以和我聊聊你的健康目标，或者分享你的心情 😊</div>
<div class="message-time">刚刚</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- 快捷建议 -->
<div class="chat-suggestions" id="chatSuggestions">
<button class="suggestion-chip" onclick="sendQuickMessage('今天运动量达标了吗？')">📊 今日运动</button>
<button class="suggestion-chip" onclick="sendQuickMessage('给我一些饮食建议')">🥗 饮食建议</button>
<button class="suggestion-chip" onclick="sendQuickMessage('我有点累了')">😴 感觉疲劳</button>
<button class="suggestion-chip" onclick="sendQuickMessage('鼓励我一下！')">💪 需要鼓励</button>
</div>

<!-- 输入区域 -->
<div class="chat-input-area">
<div class="input-wrapper">
<input type="text" class="chat-input" id="chatInput" placeholder="输入消息..." onkeypress="if(event.key==='Enter')sendChatMessage()">
<button class="send-btn" onclick="sendChatMessage()">➤</button>
</div>
<div class="input-hint">💡 提示: 你可以问我关于运动、饮食、睡眠的任何问题</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- ========== 设置页 ========== -->
<div class="page" id="settingsPage">
<div class="profile-page">
<div class="page-header" style="padding-top: 60px;">
